    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Computer graphics technology as applied to special effects for motion pictures. The term is used generally to refer to images that mimic the appearance of three dimensional objects.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
